[[File:NetRadiant-start.png|thumb|right|The starting layout of NetRadiant]]

NetRadiant is a map editor for the [[w:id tech 3|id tech 3]] or [[w:id tech 4|id tech 4]] engines. It is a fork of [[GtkRadiant]], and has more features added for newer games such as [[w:Xonotic|Xonotic]] and [[w:Warsow (video game)|Warsow]]. It comes with the [[Q3Map2]] BSP compiler.

Although this book has been written using Xonotic as an example, other games should be similar.

