{{Goodbook|edit={{{edit|}}}|box={{{box|}}}
 |title=A-level Computing/AQA
 |cover=<!-- the name of the image to use for the thumbnail -->
 |desc=[[A-level Computing/AQA]] is an A level computing book which aims to fit in with the AQA GCE A-Level Computing syllabus but is not endorsed by AQA. It should be useful as a revision guide or to find alternative explanations to the ones in your textbook.

