==About this page==
This is an incomplete list of faulty assets found on the DLS in fresh downloads. It is subject to change and rapid changes at that. The hope is by providing  a public list of what needs fixed that is accessible both in web searching and to those involved in the DLS Cleanup efforts, we can better guide and expedite the cleansing faulty content so it stops biting users.

==How to prepare data entries==
The template takes three placeholder arguments or parameters and was purpose defined to make it easy to convert'' 'cut buffer captured' lists'' of {{TBS|username}},<KUID:xxx:yyy> information as {{TL|Content Manager}} presents in its main view pane.
;The process
: ''The process assumes {{TA|Notepad++}} or other program editor supporting REGEX search and replace (SAR)''.
# Capture a batch of assets from CM and paste into a temporary or log file.
# normal mode SAR ',<' and replace with '|<'
# REGEX mode SAR '^(\w*}' and replace with '{{TRS-FA-Te|'
# REGEX mode SAR to '$' and replace with '}}'
# paste the assembled template calls within the template call shell
{{Trainz-stub}}

