{{question-answer|question=2. <math> (x^2)- 3x - 10 \,</math>|answer={{noprint|<math>(x-5)(x+2)</math>}}}}

{{question-answer|question=2. <math> (x^2)-12x + 32 \,</math>|answer={{noprint|<math>(x-4)(x-8)</math>}}}}


=====Inequalities=====

